reviewText: And here I thought mine was a mistake when there was only one disc for Alexander. Obviously everybody else had the same problem. How could Warner be so shoddy? I guess they simply don't care. This item should be taken off the market.
Troy was complete, but only disc 1 of the 2 needed to view Alexander in its entirety.

second half dvd of alexander revisited was not included.
